[^CHRISTIAN MEETS THREE SHINING ONES.^]

<P 37>
   [$I saw then in my Dream that 
he went on thus, even untill he 
came at a bottom, where he saw, 
a little out of the way, three Men 
fast asleep with Fetters upon their 
