my certain going in after it: all 
which things I doubt you want, and 
want them, because you came not 
in at the Gate.
 
[^CHRISTIAN GOES UP THE HILL CALLED DIFFICULTY.^]
  
<P 44>
   [$Now when he was got up to the 
