is fear of death, and life everlasting 
beyond it. I will yet go forward. [$So 
(^Mistrust^) and (^Timorus^) ran down 
the Hill; and (^Christian^) went on his 
way.$] [^...^]

[^CHRISTIAN LOSES HIS ROLL, AND HAS TO GO BACK TO FIND IT.^]

